Integer.Name: DmaEngineMaxQueueSize
Integer.ToolTip: Maximum number of pending buffers (i.e., buffers queued for DMA operations)
Integer.Description: Maximum number of pending buffers (i.e., buffers queued for DMA operations). Pending buffers are removed from the input queue and placed in an internal pending buffer queue.
